  "title": "URGENT: System Integration IT Specialist (medical)",
  "description": "<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li><p>Own and deliver healthcare ICT projects from requirements to deployment and support</p></li><li><p>Lead IT solution scoping, presentations, and implementation</p></li><li><p>Work with customer IT teams to integrate solutions into their environments (networks, systems, security)</p></li><li><p>Support sales activities including RFPs, tenders, and proposals</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with global solution teams (USA/Japan) on enterprise IT solutions</p></li><li><p>Train channel partners on ICT solutions.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>What You Bring</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Health Informatics, IT, Computer Science, Biomedical Engineering, or related field</p></li><li><p>2 years’ experience in healthcare IT, clinical informatics, or medical device integration</p></li><li><p>Hands-on exposure to HL7, EMR/EHR integrations</p></li><li><p>Basic SQL and scripting skills (Python/Java an advantage)</p></li><li><p>Strong communication skills and ability to work independently</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg </p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: John Angeline</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1544851</p>",
